ar Agarwal on June 25, 1965 and is headquartered in Panaji, India.\n\nTL;DR Puts\n\nLooking for more companies that hit this matrix of manufacturing  and energy exposure with really poor credit ratings. Think these are companies that will go down/implode.  Anyone have thoughts???", "created_utc": 1583521635.0, "permalink": "/r/wallstreetbets/comments/feidqv/vedanta_indian_manufacturing_company_may_be_among/", "is_self": true}